snippet.title: Bonfire Peaks - Announcement Trailer (Indie Puzzle Game)
snippet.description:
Bonfire Peaks is a difficult open world puzzle game about attachment by Corey Martin, creator of Pipe Push Paradise and Hiding Spot.

Coming later this year to PC, Mac & Linux.
http://bonfirepeaks.com

Things you do in Bonfire Peaks:
- Climb mysterious ruins
- Set fire to your belongings
- Indulge your feelings
- Carry things
- Let go of things
